{
  "stem": "15396.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, we kept hearing-- and then I heard firsthand from-- a couple of things like the night of crystal thing and, you know, there's all the dreadful things that the Jew-- that the were-- Jews were having done to them by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was well-publicized in various aspects of the press, and completely ignored by others.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if you-- if you read carefully, you saw practically everything that was happening in Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were some very well-informed people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, by that time, I was-- my friends were mostly a little bit older than I was, and I was striking up some friendships with journalists and people like that, and musicians, of course.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was crazy about music always.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, most of those being Jewish, naturally, I could hear from a lot of them what was happening.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then you'd run into people like-- people who were leaving, leaving Paris, not leaving Europe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then Belgium, I-- I met two or three people in Belgium who were-- couldn't wait to get out, and they were saying exactly, we're going to get out and we're going to get everybody we can out.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, before the war started, we knew very, very well that-- that the Jews were going to have one hell of a time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very, very obvious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it was happening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean it wasn't going to have, it was happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was obvious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you couldn't help but see it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was-- You know, I think everybody has to have something really passionate in their life that they feel very passionately about.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, I have my wife, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was the thing that really turned me on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And partly--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't know how.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
